snippet.title: Angry Birds Evolution | Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Angry Birds are back! Build your team, train your birds and kick the pigs off Bird Island. Choose your favorites from over 100 ALL-NEW BIRDS in this action packed RPG with superb 3D graphics. Mayhem! Drama! Hilarious Fun! Join the craze today!

▶︎ Play Angry Birds Evolution:
http://rov.io/PlayEvolution_yt
